{"timeRating":"II","description":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><p>A short canyon with a drop overlooking the 405 near the Getty Center. The rappel can be easily seen from the northbound lanes of the 405.\n<\/p>\n<meta property=\"mw:PageProp\/toc\" \/>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Approach\">Approach<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>Park at the end of Bundy Drive and take the trail up to Mt Saint Mary's Fire Road, then follow the firebreak to the drop-in. Alternately, parking at Mt Saint Mary's could cut off some elevation gain. The shortest approach of all would be if you could find a way to park near the bottom of the canyon, but the area is mainly devoted to the Getty Center and parking may not be possible.\n<\/p>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Descent\">Descent<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>The descent is quick going and mostly brush-free. The one mandatory rappel near the end can be anchored from a tree DCR. There are a few downclimbs on smooth black rock after this, then you emerge in the drainage basin next to the 405.\n<\/p>\n<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r1062633282\">@media all and (max-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .content .thumb>div:not(.thumbinner){display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-content:flex-start;flex-direction:column}}body.skin-vector .mw-parser-output div.thumb>div:not(.thumbinner){font-size:94%;text-align:center;overflow:hidden;min-width:100px}body.skin-minerva .mw-parser-output div.thumb>div:not(.thumbinner){margin:0 auto;max-width:100%!important}<\/style> \n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div style=\"display:table;\">\n<span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\/Frameless\">\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Exit\">Exit<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>If you parked on Bundy or Mt Saint Mary's, climb the ridge just north of the canyon to get back to the firebreak. It's steep going at first but gets easier with animal trails the higher you go.\n<\/p>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1062633282\"> \n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div style=\"display:table;\">\n<span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\/Frameless\">\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Red_tape\">Red tape<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Beta_sites\">Beta sites<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Trip_reports_and_media\">Trip reports and media<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Background\">Background<\/h2><\/div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw‐api‐ext.codfw.main‐6779cc57fc‐pwh8d\nCached time: 20240914191911\nCache expiry: 2592000\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.037 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.044 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 207\/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1324\/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 78\/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8\/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0\/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0\/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1058\/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.003\/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 635189\/52428800 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0\/400\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   32.347      1 -total\n 99.60%   32.216      2 Template:Pic\n 51.61%   16.695      2 Template:Str_number\/trim\n-->\n<\/div>","id":66428,"riskRating":null,"permit":"No","rappelCountMax":1,"quality":0,"geojson":null,"months":[],"url":"https:\/\/ropewiki.com\/405_Canyon","vehicle":null,"technicalRating":3,"rappelCountMin":1,"shuttleSeconds":null,"longitude":-118.4775,"name":"405 Canyon","waterRating":"A","version":"9730c3ff63cd1c495328c5209d9924cbed5b2bb0df2b202c84c4d621f9a271f4","rappelLongestMeters":15.24,"latitude":34.0929}